Clefable (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0035: Clefairy
Pokémon
#0037: Vulpix →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Clefable (TCG Pocket).

Clefable has been featured on 22 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Clefable cards are normally Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Clefable

Clefable
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
